## Belluno Cafe — Website Plan

A multi-page, motion-rich website for **Belluno** (cafe in Vesu, Surat — @belluno.vesu) inspired by Italian alpine luxury: Verde Alpi marble, antique gold, cream, with a single electric-blue signature accent.

### Pages

```text
/             Home          — bento grid hero, signature picks, story snippet, hours+map tile
/menu         Menu          — full menu in categories (coffee, espresso, signature, food, desserts)
/about        Our Story     — brand story, philosophy, Vesu roots
/gallery      Gallery       — masonry photo grid of cafe + drinks
/contact      Visit Us      — address, hours, phone, embedded Google Map (link below)
/reservations Reserve       — simple booking form (name, date, time, party size, notes)
```

Google Maps link wired into Contact + home location tile: https://maps.app.goo.gl/QFYGZavcNMqiqM8T6

### Visual System (locked)

- **Palette:** `#233F31` deep verde alpi (primary), `#607164` sage marble, `#F3ECDC` warm cream (surface), `#BB9A64` antique gold (accent), `#4E73F5` electric blue (rare signature mark only)
- **Type:** DM Serif Display (headings) + Fira Sans (body), loaded via `<link>` in `__root.tsx`
- **Layout:** Asymmetric bento grid on home; editorial layouts elsewhere
- **Tokens:** Defined in `src/styles.css` under `@theme` (no hardcoded color classes)

### Animation (maximum intensity)

- Letter-by-letter serif headline reveals on load and scroll
- Scroll-linked parallax on hero marble texture + image zoom in bento tiles
- Hover tilts and lifts on tiles, magnetic CTA buttons
- Page transitions with mask wipes between routes
- Subtle film-grain + marble veining overlays
- Implemented with Framer Motion (`motion` package) + native CSS scroll-driven animations
- Honors `prefers-reduced-motion`

### Routes & Components

```text
src/routes/
  __root.tsx          shared nav + footer, font <link>s, page transitions
  index.tsx           home (bento grid)
  menu.tsx
  about.tsx
  gallery.tsx
  contact.tsx
  reservations.tsx

src/components/
  layout/Nav.tsx, Footer.tsx, PageTransition.tsx
  motion/RevealText.tsx, TiltCard.tsx, MagneticButton.tsx, MarbleBackdrop.tsx
  home/HeroBento.tsx, SignatureTile.tsx, StoryTile.tsx, LocationTile.tsx, HoursTile.tsx, GalleryTeaser.tsx
  menu/MenuSection.tsx, MenuItem.tsx
