### Content

- Realistic placeholder copy crafted from Instagram cues (specialty coffee, brunch, cozy alpine vibe in Vesu)
- AI-generated imagery for hero, ambience, drinks, pastries (Italian cafe / verde alpi marble theme)
- Menu items as plausible Italian cafe offerings — easy to edit later
- All "Order"/"Reserve" CTAs functional within site (reservations form shows success toast; no backend)

### Technical notes

- Stack: TanStack Start (existing), Tailwind v4, shadcn, Framer Motion
- Add deps: `motion` (Framer Motion v11)
- Per-route `head()` with unique title/description/OG for SEO
- Single H1 per page, semantic HTML, alt text on all images
- No backend / Cloud needed — reservations form is a frontend-only demo (can be wired later)

### Out of scope (for now)

- Real reservations backend, payment, online ordering
- CMS for menu (menu lives in a typed data file `src/data/menu.ts`)
- Instagram live feed (use static curated images)
